SELECT c.customer_name, MIN(p.price) AS min_price FROM Customers c JOIN Orders o ON c.customer_id = o.customer_id JOIN Products p ON o.product_id = p.id GROUP BY c.customer_name HAVING MIN(p.price) < 50;

SELECT c.customer_name, p.name, COUNT(o.order_id) AS total_orders FROM Customers c JOIN Orders o ON c.customer_id = o.customer_id JOIN Products p ON o.product_id = p.id GROUP BY c.customer_name, p.name HAVING COUNT(o.order_id) > 1;
